00:27:38.160 --> 00:27:39.830
Lo siento...

00:27:41.150 --> 00:27:43.490
por recordar demasiado tarde.

00:27:45.140 --> 00:27:47.040
No es demasiado tarde.

00:27:49.040 --> 00:27:50.390
Entonces...

00:27:51.370 --> 00:27:53.150
ven despacio.

00:27:54.890 --> 00:27:56.730
Y no te caigas.

00:28:02.220 --> 00:28:04.200
Antes de eso,

00:28:04.200 --> 00:28:06.810
